creator: Designs for Health, Inc.
descriptionHtml:
The West Clinic app is an easy to use tool that helps our patients stay connected to us, get needed support between visits and most importantly get their health back.

Designed with our mission of creating energy, longevity and balance in the lives of all our patients, this app transforms the patient experience by giving you (right on your phone) everything needed to stay focused and informed about your highly personalized program.

Simply download the app and login to see the program we customized specifically for you in our office so we can help you eliminate the uncertainty of what to do when you get home.

No more guessing which supplements to take and when. No more guessing which foods you should be eating and which foods you should not be eating to get the best results with your specific health challenges. No more guessing if you are on the right track because we have taken the guess work out of it for you.

This easy to use app has you tracking your daily progress in each area we are working on together like food, supplements, movement, sleep, meditation and more.

Includes your personalized meal plan complete with all the recipes, weekly grocery shopping lists and printable guides to simplify your life while giving you victory over the battle with food.

Have you ever left a doctors office feeling overwhelmed and disappointed in not knowing exactly what to do to conquer your health problems? Well this app helps us help you not feel that way anymore by simplifying your life and helping to make adjustments along the journey. The West Clinic team has committed to be there with you every step of the way on your road back to energy, longevity and balance!

Designed with our mission of creating energy, longevity and balance in the lives of all our patients, this app transforms the patient experience by giving you (right on your phone) everything needed to stay focused and informed about your highly personalized program.

Simply download the app and login to see the program we customized specifically for you in our office so we can help you eliminate the uncertainty of what to do when you get home.

No more guessing which supplements to take and when. No more guessing which foods you should be eating and which foods you should not be eating to get the best results with your specific health challenges. No more guessing if you are on the right track because we have taken the guess work out of it for you.

This easy to use app has you tracking your daily progress in each area we are working on together like food, supplements, movement, sleep, meditation and more.

Includes your personalized meal plan complete with all the recipes, weekly grocery shopping lists and printable guides to simplify your life while giving you victory over the battle with food.

Have you ever left a doctors office feeling overwhelmed and disappointed in not knowing exactly what to do to conquer your health problems? Well this app helps us help you not feel that way anymore by simplifying your life and helping to make adjustments along the journey. The West Clinic team has committed to be there with you every step of the way on your road back to energy, longevity and balance!
